		"description": "This folder contains examples on how to login to REST Server API and create / delete a trigger.\n\n**Create Trigger (File Upload Event Type)**\n\nSteps to acheive it\n\n1. Get CSRF token before login (API - Get CSRF token before login).\n2. Login into MFT server (API - Login request ).\n3. Get CSRF token after login (API - Get CSRF token after login).\n4. Create Trigger (API - Create trigger ).\n5. Logout from MFT Server (API - Logout request ).\n    \n\n**Delete Trigger**\n\nSteps to acheive it\n\n1. Get CSRF token before login (API - Get CSRF token before login).\n2. Login into MFT server (API - Login request ).\n3. Get CSRF token after login (API - Get CSRF token after login).\n4. Delete Trigger (API - Delete trigger ).\n5. Logout from MFT Server (API - Logout request ).",
